ji\" /> <br />\n咪講左civil大部分都要落site囉<br />\n點都多人過cu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又搬龍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一時又用港大中大科大話CUengine三大最低分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到科大QSA收17分就話用engine去比<br />\n（笑撚到三間大學同一科比緊係有最高同最低架喇，唔通我又好似你個傻仔咁日日開post回post笑ust science咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n一時又話CU冇civil落乜地盤，<span style=\"color: red;\">明明成句講緊冇civil就唔會落地盤</span><br />\n到人地笑鳩佢唔一定civil先可以落地盤<br />\n跟住又兜話我知ee同telecom會落地盤呀<br />\n不過依家講緊中大engine唔係大部份都落地盤<br />\n<br />\n好喇被人反駁按照呢個邏輯科大都唔係『大部分人』落地盤<br />\n又搬龍門話科大有civil，點都多人過Cu engine落地盤<br />\n<br />\n邊有人夠你玩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa1dc1293b6070bcf53dfeba194c74bf5e74da4","tid":478741,"uid":34884,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T13:27:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連科垃圾civil都冇<br />\n中大垃圾都不如呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：hku</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問心如果夠分入HKU UST engine， <br />\n點會揀入CU engine 啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀engine緊係hku ust poly<br />\ncu engine根本唔入流<br />\n睇個分就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再睇埋樓主呢個人辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n緊係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有全港排名、資源、學術第一第二既電子工程唔讀